    </item>
    <item>
      <title>[부음] 김문영씨 별세 외</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/10/01/6VL57J64AREHBKGEU4HWMVI5WA/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2024/10/01/6VL57J64AREHBKGEU4HWMVI5WA/</guid>
